'''Turummes''' were distant relatives of the [[farumme]]s, both [[Reptile/Legends|reptiles]] and native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Adumar/Legends|Adumar]]. They dug elaborate nests in the ground, which prompted the [[Adumari]] to call the apartment quarters built below the surface "[[turumme-warrens]]."

